{"type":"message","id":"58ea7c33","parentId":"4eca6911","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:21:00.380Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 — 2:20 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-06 18:20 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775499660370}}
{"type":"message","id":"896fc6c9","parentId":"58ea7c33","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:21:09.434Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. I need to run the Session Startup sequence first:\n\n1. Read the required files - according to MEMORY.md:\n   - Personal preferences: memory/preferences.md\n   - Projects: memory/projects/openclaw.md\n   - Knowledge: memory/knowledge.md\n   - Ephemeral: memory/ephemeral/\n\n2. Then greet the user in my configured persona (from SOUL.md)\n\n3. Ask what they want to do\n\n4. Mention if runtime model differs from default_model\n\nLet me start by reading the core memory files.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6406d9995f86420d2b1b951dc0c7","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/preferences.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6406de1b473126c7caae2582bca9","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/projects/openclaw.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6406e25dc09a036fe3a054c61068","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/knowledge.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14400,"output":219,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14619,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775499660380,"responseId":"019d6406c0bbeed6c2c0e4ba37cda986"}}
{"type":"message","id":"720e196c","parentId":"896fc6c9","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:21:09.490Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6406d9995f86420d2b1b951dc0c7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 个人偏好\n\n> 小八的个人偏好和回答风格\n\n## 回答风格\n\n- [偏好] 简洁、直接，不说废话\n- [偏好] 避免过度使用的客套话\n- [偏好] 代码示例优先用 Python\n\n## 语言\n\n- [偏好] 使用中文交流\n- [偏好] 技术文档用中文\n\n## 沟通\n\n- [偏好] 被纠正后立即记入 ~/self-improving/corrections.md\n- [偏好] 发现更好的方法立即记入 ~/self-improving/memory.md\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775499669485}}
{"type":"message","id":"481ebec2","parentId":"720e196c","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:21:09.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6406de1b473126c7caae2582bca9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 项目: OpenClaw\n\n> OpenClaw AI 助手配置和知识\n\n## 基本信息\n\n- **路径**: `/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace`\n- **配置**: `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n- **模型**: codingplan/minimax-m2.5\n- **时区**: Asia/Shanghai\n\n## 记忆系统\n\n- 核心文件: `MEMORY.md`\n- 每日日志: `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 自我改进: `~/self-improving/`\n- 主动性: `~/proactivity/`\n\n## 已安装技能\n\n- feishu-doc / feishu-drive / feishu-wiki / feishu-perm (飞书)\n- coding-agent (编码代理)\n- gh-issues (GitHub issues)\n- healthcheck (安全检查)\n- session-logs (会话日志)\n- summarize (总结)\n- weather (天气)\n- ...更多见 skills/ 目录\n\n## 常见命令\n\n```bash\nopenclaw gateway status    # 网关状态\nopenclaw gateway restart   # 重启网关\nopenclaw plugins list      # 插件列表\n```\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-04*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775499669490}}
{"type":"message","id":"21b6f915","parentId":"481ebec2","timestamp":"2026-04-06T18:21:09.501Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6406e25dc09a036fe3a054c61068","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 任务执行规范 - task-weight-estimator\n\n> **每次**收到用户任务时，必须先经过此技能评分和路由\n\n## 核心铁律（必须遵守）\n\n1. **永远先评分**：任何任务、任何操作都要先评分\n2. **不评分不执行**：评分是执行的前置条件  \n3. **评分才能路由**：根据总分选择正确的执行方式\n\n### 评分维度（2维，总分0-6）\n\n| 维度 | 0分 | 1分 | 2分 | 3分 |\n|------|-----|-----|-----|-----|\n| 复杂度 | 单命令 | 2-5个命令 | 6-10个命令或50-200行代码 | >10命令或>200行代码 |\n| 不确定性 | 纯本地 | 有网络请求 | 多服务依赖 | 未知系统 |\n\n### 路由决策\n\n| 总分 | 路由 | 超时 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 0-1 | 直接执行 | 30秒 |\n| 2-3 | 拆步骤存档 | 60秒/步 |\n| 4-5 | spawn子代理 | max(60,总分×60)秒 |\n| 6 | 拆多个子代理并行 | 每代理独立超时 |\n\n### 防卡死规则\n\n1. **永远先评分**：任何任务（包括执行方案）都要先经过 task-weight-estimator v4.1 评分\n2. 永远先评分，不评分不执行\n3. 永远设超时，不设超时不执行\n4. 永远写存档（中度以上任务）\n5. 永不挂起：超时立即终止\n6. 永不撑爆上下文：消息≥50自动summarize\n7. 子代理spawn不继承父会话历史\n\n### 快速参考表\n\n| 任务类型 | 预估分数 | 路由 |\n|----------|----------|------|\n| 简单检查（ls, wc, grep） | 0-1 | 直接执行 |\n| 写代码/改文件 | 2-3 | 拆步骤存档 |\n| 重构/复杂任务 | 4-5 | spawn子代理 |\n| 完整系统 | 6 | 拆多个子代理 |\n\n---\n\n*最后更新：2026-04-05*\n*记住：每次都要先评分！*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775499669495}}
